summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting the redevelopment proposal of the African-American Community Health Network to purchase and develop Parcel 23-23A in the Yesler-Atlantic Neighborhood Improvement Project (Wash. R-5) area; authorizing the Director of the Office of Housing to execute and deliver contracts and deeds; authorizing the Director of the Office of Housing to administer the "Contract for Sale of Land"; designating the disposition of sales proceeds; and ratifying and confirming prior actions.
